parameters:
\N<Rame>Those people are bullying the new girl who just arrived
here. I hate that kind of thing... I don't want to see it.
Let's go, Riia-chan.
\N<Riia>Stop it already, what's so fun about doing such things?
\N<Boy>Shut up, Riia. It's none of your business, go away.

\N<Boy>That's right, that's right, you should just quietly flirt
with that girl! Don't stick your nose in our business!

\N<Riia>Sure, that girl and I aren't friends... but it's not like it
doesn't concern me. After all, I can't just turn a blind eye
to you guys treating her badly.

\N<Fubii>What did you say? What does that mean? Can you say that
again?

\N<Boy>Hey, Riia, what are you going to do about this? It's your
fault she got away.

\N<Riia>I'm not going to do anything. Because there's no need for me
to apologize to you guys.

\N<Boy>What's that supposed to mean? Acting all high and mighty for
helping out someone like her.
\N<Riia>It's not like that. Let's go, Rame-chan.

\N<Fubii>Wait a second. Do you think it's okay to talk to me like
that? If you're going to apologize, now's the time.
\N<Rame>Apologize... but Riia-chan hasn't done anything wrong...

\N<Fubii>Even so. You opposed me... that's what you need to apologize
for.
\N<Luda Soldier>Can't you see? I'm studying, so don't talk to me...
\N<Luda Soldier>Can't you see? I'm studying right now, don't talk to me...

\N<Luda Soldier>What am I even doing here... To become a soldier of Luda?
Or maybe...

\N<Luda Soldier>Who's there...? If you have no business, please go that way.
I don't want to be seen by the Luda soldiers.
\N<Luda Soldier>Can't you see? I'm studying right now, don't talk to me...
